OL,3,C#2.1m to be spent on flood defences at
OL,4,Charbour in Guernsey
OL,6,FProgressing new flood defences for
OL,7,FBraye du Valle is vital for the future
OL,8,Fof the island's housing plans, 's
OL,9,FScrutiny Management Committee (SMC)
OL,10,Fhas been told.
OL,12,FIt comes as plans for the Leale's Yard
OL,13,F, where over 300 homes were earmarked,
OL,14,Fwere held up due to concerns over
OL,15,Fflooding.
OL,17,FBut now that access plans have been
OL,18,Fconfirmed for Leale's Yard, updated
OL,19,Fflood defences for St Sampson Harbour
OL,20,Fwill be drawn up.
