OL,3,C#2.1m to be spent on flood defences at
OL,4,Charbour in Guernsey
OL,6,FAt the recent scrutiny review, the SMC
OL,7,Fwas told that flood walls are
OL,8,Fprojected to cost #2.1m to design and
OL,9,Fimplement.
OL,11,FThe walls are expected to be planted
OL,12,Fat knee height, running along The
OL,13,FBridge frontage, and defences will
OL,14,Fhave a 50-year lifespan.
OL,16,FDirector of Environment and
OL,17,FInfrastructure Claire Barrett said:
OL,18,F"It's basically the same design as
OL,19,Fbefore.
