OL,3,C#2.1m to be spent on flood defences at
OL,4,Charbour in Guernsey
OL,6,F"It's not starting from scratch but
OL,7,Fupdating the details on that and
OL,8,Fimplementation."
OL,10,FShe added that ground would be broken
OL,11,Fonce a business case was outlined for
OL,12,Ffunding as well as an updated design
OL,13,Fplan.
OL,15,FDeputy Lindsay De Sausmarez hopes that
OL,16,Fflood defences will reassure property
OL,17,Fdevelopers that the area will be
OL,18,Fprotected, saying that "we don't want
OL,19,Fto hold up housing sites".
