OL,3,C#2.1m to be spent on flood defences at
OL,4,Charbour in Guernsey
OL,6,FCurrently, there is a 1% risk of the
OL,7,Farea being inundated with flooding
OL,8,Fevery year.
OL,10,FWhile this is low, Deputy De Sausmarez
OL,11,Fwarned that this could increase with
OL,12,Fclimate change and that a flooding
OL,13,Fevent would be severe.
OL,15,FShe added: "Irrespective of any new
OL,16,Fdevelopments that are coming forward,
OL,17,Fwe already have a significant number
OL,18,Fof private dwellings, commercial
OL,19,Fproperties, and critical
OL,20,Finfrastructure that we want to protect
OL,21,Fadequately."
